{"lemma":"مَرْجِعُ","slug":"مَرْجِعُ","root":"ر.ج.ع","root_slug":"ر-ج-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ج-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَرْجِع","root":"رجع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":16},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14905","n14906","n14907"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%AC%D9%90%D8%B9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"recourse, retreat"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"recourse, retreat; reference (like under this page), resource","tags":["especially"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"marja'"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"A unit of area equivalent in Granada to 528.42 m²","tags":["Morocco","al-Andalus"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/mar.d͡ʒiʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14905","headword_ar":"مَرْجِعٌ","root":"rjE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of the intrans. verb"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajaEa","text_ar":"رَجَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S, Msb, K, &c.) ―         -b2-  [Hence it signifies sometimes (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Recourse."},{"kind":"text","text":"See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaAbN","text_ar":"مَنَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nwb","text_ar":"نوب"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place to which a person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing, returns after going or moving therefrom;"},{"kind":"text","text":"agreeably with analogy. See an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoDarN","text_ar":"مَحْضَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marojiEu Alkatifi","text_ar":"مَرْجِعُ الكَتِفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lower part of the shoulderblade,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next the arm-pit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that on the left side being"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the region where the heart beats;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkatifi","text_ar":"الكَتِفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajoEu","text_ar":"رَجْعُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marojiEu Almirofaqi","text_ar":"مَرْجِعُ المِرْفَقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place to which the elbow returns when, after it has been removed from its usual place, it is brought back thereto;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which place"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a beast is next the arm-pit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariySN","text_ar":"فَرِيصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places]: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraAjiEu","text_ar":"مَرَاجِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marojiEN","text_ar":"مَرْجِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing, to which a person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing, is referred, as his,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its, source:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoSibN","text_ar":"مَنْصِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-  Also, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, to which a person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing, returns."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b5-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result, to which a person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing, ultimately,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eventually, comes. A goal."},{"kind":"text","text":"]       -A3-  It is also an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajaEahu","text_ar":"رَجَعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n14906","headword_ar":"مُرْجِعٌ","root":"rjE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":",] applied to a she-camel, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Becoming in good condition after leanness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, TA.) [See 4, of which it is the act. part. n.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA mataAEN murojiEN","text_ar":"هٰذَا مَتَاعٌ مُرْجِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is a commodity for which there will be a return,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"profit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saforapN murojiEapN","text_ar":"سَفْرَةٌ مُرْجِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A journey having a recompense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reward, and a good issue"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n14907","headword_ar":"مُرَجَّعٌ","root":"rjE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajiyEN","text_ar":"رَجِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; first sentence."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}